1974;;The Crazy World of Julius Vrooder;;American;;Arthur Hiller;;Timothy Bottoms, Barbara Hershey, Albert Salmi, George Marshall;;unknown;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Crazy_World_of_Julius_Vrooder;;A Vietnam veteran who lives at the V.A. Hospital escapes and builds an underground fortress next to the highway. He keeps it decent and plans some other actions, including getting free light and phone service. While a few people and the police try to find him, Vrooder finds love with a doctor, Zanni.